  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras/b8dd89573357d788807f7f6f97e76141.avif?t=1734071462\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras_big/b8dd89573357d788807f7f6f97e76141.avif?t=1734071462 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We have created a single-player deck-building game following the classic formula of deck-building roguelikes. Choose your protagonist, collect cards, defeat enemies, and explore dungeons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras/28ed97e1221b9e95b44e251010cb293c.avif?t=1734071462\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras_big/28ed97e1221b9e95b44e251010cb293c.avif?t=1734071462 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Features</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras/ad42fe1c0ae76855288af93e63c7820b.avif?t=1734071462\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras_big/ad42fe1c0ae76855288af93e63c7820b.avif?t=1734071462 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Build your own deck: Win battles, collect a variety of cards through events and shops, and create your unique build to conquer the dungeons with the cards you choose!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras/f59772cb4b7d9e7f774c401d6d363abe.avif?t=1734071462\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras_big/f59772cb4b7d9e7f774c401d6d363abe.avif?t=1734071462 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Enjoy spectacular battles created with a combination of pixel graphics and 3D effects!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras/7b8f127c62a5d6cb93a59d4e90c5b53f.avif?t=1734071462\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras_big/7b8f127c62a5d6cb93a59d4e90c5b53f.avif?t=1734071462 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Capture monsters: Use capture cards to tame monsters and add them to your party to gain various beneficial effects!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras/c6744404d6c373fa79d54a7be662ec94.avif?t=1734071462\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras_big/c6744404d6c373fa79d54a7be662ec94.avif?t=1734071462 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Discover powerful relics: Collect relics that grant advantageous effects in battle through events and boss fights. But remember, there's no gain without pain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Early Access</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The Early Access version currently supports one character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- We have completed the battle cards and combat system for this character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Over 25 unique job-specific cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- More than 10 unique dungeon events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Over 40 unique monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- More than 40 unique monster cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Card banning system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Card preservation system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Monster capture system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are a small team continuing to research and develop this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras/b8dd89573357d788807f7f6f97e76141.avif?t=1734071462\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras_big/b8dd89573357d788807f7f6f97e76141.avif?t=1734071462 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We have created a single-player deck-building game following the classic formula of deck-building roguelikes. Choose your protagonist, collect cards, defeat enemies, and explore dungeons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras/28ed97e1221b9e95b44e251010cb293c.avif?t=1734071462\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras_big/28ed97e1221b9e95b44e251010cb293c.avif?t=1734071462 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Features</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras/ad42fe1c0ae76855288af93e63c7820b.avif?t=1734071462\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras_big/ad42fe1c0ae76855288af93e63c7820b.avif?t=1734071462 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Build your own deck: Win battles, collect a variety of cards through events and shops, and create your unique build to conquer the dungeons with the cards you choose!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras/f59772cb4b7d9e7f774c401d6d363abe.avif?t=1734071462\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras_big/f59772cb4b7d9e7f774c401d6d363abe.avif?t=1734071462 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Enjoy spectacular battles created with a combination of pixel graphics and 3D effects!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras/7b8f127c62a5d6cb93a59d4e90c5b53f.avif?t=1734071462\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras_big/7b8f127c62a5d6cb93a59d4e90c5b53f.avif?t=1734071462 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Capture monsters: Use capture cards to tame monsters and add them to your party to gain various beneficial effects!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras/c6744404d6c373fa79d54a7be662ec94.avif?t=1734071462\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367260/extras_big/c6744404d6c373fa79d54a7be662ec94.avif?t=1734071462 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Discover powerful relics: Collect relics that grant advantageous effects in battle through events and boss fights. But remember, there's no gain without pain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Early Access</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The Early Access version currently supports one character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- We have completed the battle cards and combat system for this character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Over 25 unique job-specific cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- More than 10 unique dungeon events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Over 40 unique monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- More than 40 unique monster cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Card banning system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Card preservation system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Monster capture system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are a small team continuing to research and develop this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
